   312 221A 6D BA 21											ADC RESBCD+3
   313 221D 8D BA 21											STA RESBCD+3
   314 2220 CA												DEX			 ;More bits to process?
   315 2221 D0 D0												BNE LOOPHEX
   316 2223 D8												CLD			 ;Leave decimal mode
   317 													;BRK
   318 2224												BCD2ATASCII
